{"tid":474920,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊大股東Naspers：無意永久持有騰訊","createTime":"2017-11-20T15:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T03:46:01.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"213f1fc90a757abd2474ebc2cc2079364a66153b","tid":474920,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"騰訊（700）大股東、南非報業集團Naspers主席Koos Bekker今日於開普敦的股東大會上表示，公司無意永久持有騰訊股份。<br />\n<br />\n據彭博報導指，Koos Bekker於會出指，現時騰訊的確為股東帶來了回報，又指「如果5年前沽出每股只能得到45元，而現在它的價格已經升到325元。」（If we had sold then, you would have gotten 45 Hong Kong dollars, now you get 325. We are not married to the share, but at this point in time it&rsquo;s paying shareholders.）<br />\n現時Naspers持有騰訊33.18%股權，以今日收市價計，市值1327億美元（約10349億港元），較Naspers的市值高出超過300億美元！<br />\n蘋果財經，關心你飯碗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170825/large/1503668380_7160.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170825%2Flarge%2F1503668380_7160.jpg&h=b92c161b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNaspers主席Koos Bekker<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20170825/57128679\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170825%2F57128679&d=y%2BRqw0hR3gSMVi7XQM28Dm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5de00622\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170825%2F57128679&h=63394e37\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20170825/57128679</a>"},{"pid":"ee83d1f3410a8c97a8a013df26791b5b09ba8b02","tid":474920,"uid":9931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"岩呀<br />\n<br />\n一生同一世都總有個日子"},{"pid":"ff869a228f31228584e1d7fa86ccf4ddc56d0868","tid":474920,"uid":47099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:24